{"tid":731291,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［肥西終於有用］比人攞去做癌症研究","createTime":"2018-07-06T05:25:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T05:25:04.000Z","uid":22365,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b53890b5b67632bc45387ebc66724f6f4c2e3d0d","tid":731291,"uid":22365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T05:25:04.000Z","msg":"【中大擬招募一萬名肥<del>胖市民</del> 西免費提供大腸癌、前列腺癌及乳癌篩查】<br />\n中文大學開展防癌計劃研究肥胖與癌症的關係，計劃會招募一萬名肥<del>胖市民</del>西，為他們免費提供大腸癌、前列腺癌及乳癌篩查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/883848431807226/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F883848431807226%2F&d=xHFVjRPohI8qIoRYiaf%2FEozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=38d4089d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/883848431807226/</a>"}]}